<paragraph blockId="6.[160,1156,1331,1461]" pageId="6">Main skeleton composed of a quite diffuse network of acanthostyles lying in bundles and disorderly scattered single spicules of the same category. Skeleton of dermal membrane consists of similar network of tylotes lying more or less tangentially.</paragraph>
